00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:02,840
 thought it should be,

271
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:06,080
 although it was exactly as God had planned it to be.

272
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:09,800
 And I think no more powerfully do they show us this

