00:12:21,800 --> 00:12:24,120
 Now, that genealogy is presented to us

279
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,520
 in both Matthew and in Luke,

280
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:27,660
 Matthew chapter one, Luke chapter three.

