00:12:54,640 --> 00:12:57,560
 the one who began Israel itself,

293
00:12:57,560 --> 00:12:59,400
 the one who was faithful to God

294
00:12:59,400 --> 00:13:03,640
 and did so many things as an act of love and grace to Him.

