00:17:15,980 --> 00:17:20,920
 You'll find characters like this,

402
00:17:20,920 --> 00:17:23,360
 like Jacob and Jeconiah,

403
00:17:23,360 --> 00:17:28,360
 who were basically serial liars and manipulative deceivers.

